- Yeah.

36
00:05:14,039 --> 00:05:17,634
I couldn't do much, you know.
It just reminded me of you.

37
00:05:22,448 --> 00:05:26,782
- OK. See if one fits.
- I love these guys.

38
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:31,647
- If one fits, can I have it?
- I'll give it to you.

39
00:05:31,824 --> 00:05:33,416
