"Because he was so small,"

51
00:06:34,353 --> 00:06:37,652
"Stuart was often hard to find
around the house. "

52
00:06:37,823 --> 00:06:43,159
"His father and his mother
and his brother George... "

53
00:06:43,328 --> 00:06:47,355
- "Seldom. "
- "... seldom could locate him"

54
00:06:47,533 --> 00:06:49,763
"by looking for him. "

55
00:06:49,935 --> 00:06:53,098
