- I'm a responsible person.

315
00:45:30,854 --> 00:45:33,322
<i>Omri, I'm down here.</i>

316
00:45:34,891 --> 00:45:36,950
- Don't touch the cupboard.
- OK.

317
00:45:40,964 --> 00:45:45,731
