It means a lot to me.

318
00:45:56,179 --> 00:45:58,272
Thank you. I heard.

319
00:46:00,450 --> 00:46:03,112
Can I see your arm? Yeah.

320
00:46:03,286 --> 00:46:06,084
You all right?
You need to wash that.

321
00:46:06,256 --> 00:46:10,556
