- Patrick is just plain defiant.

323
00:46:22,572 --> 00:46:24,699
- No! No!
- Yes!

324
00:46:24,874 --> 00:46:26,205
It's not a game!

325
00:46:30,847 --> 00:46:32,940
Slow down!

326
00:46:45,695 --> 00:46:48,755
God-dang it! Put me down!

327
00:46:48,932 --> 00:46:51,400
Dang... tarnation.

328
00:46:52,435 --> 00:46:55,097
No more. I promise no more.

329
00:46:55,271 --> 00:46:58,001
Oh, dog! Not another drop.

330
00:46:58,174 --> 00:47:01,473
- He's mine.
- Shut your eyes! Watch out, Patrick!

331
00:47:01,644 --> 00:47:04,340
Get back. Come on.

332
00:47:04,814 --> 00:47:07,180
He shot me! He shot me!

333
00:47:07,350 --> 00:47:12,219
Deliriums! Hell-fire and damnation!
