339
00:47:30,373 --> 00:47:34,104
- I can't believe it. This is great.
- This is not so great.

340
00:47:34,277 --> 00:47:37,440
This has got to be a delirium!
Where's my hat?

341
00:47:37,614 --> 00:47:39,980
- He can't stay here.
- I want to keep him.

342
00:47:40,149 --> 00:47:44,108
- I've lost my hat!
- Can we send him back?

343
00:47:44,287 --> 00:47:45,982
I'm comin' to get you, Darlin'!

344
00:47:46,689 --> 00:47:47,986
I want him!

345
00:47:48,157 --> 00:47:51,217
Not one more drop as long as I live.

346
00:47:52,729 --> 00:47:55,289
Oh, my dear sweet Lord!

347
00:47:55,465 --> 00:47:57,126
I need a drink.

348
00:47:58,201 --> 00:48:01,728
This is just gettin'
worse by the minute.

349
00:48:01,904 --> 00:48:03,872
What's your name?

350
