415
00:56:09,825 --> 00:56:12,658
- He can go, I can go.
- It's too risky.

416
00:56:12,828 --> 00:56:14,796
- Whiskey?
- Risky! Dangerous!

417
00:56:14,964 --> 00:56:18,331
Good. I like danger.
Do you like danger, Texas man?

418
00:56:18,501 --> 00:56:22,494
