440
00:58:21,657 --> 00:58:24,490
<i>I thought America should
be green and yellow.</i>

441
00:58:24,660 --> 00:58:27,857
<i>Loretta thought it
should be more like beige...</i>

442
00:58:28,030 --> 00:58:30,362
What are these folks talking about?

443
00:58:30,532 --> 00:58:34,798
<i>- .. to make it more topo...
- Topographical.</i>

444
00:58:35,638 --> 00:58:39,005
Sounds to me like they've
been hitting the old tornado juice.

445
00:58:43,112 --> 00:58:46,479
You ever been west
of the Mississippi?

446
00:58:50,786 --> 00:58:52,253
Big river?

447
00:58:55,357 --> 00:58:57,154
I have travelled to the far north.

448
00:58:58,627 --> 00:59:02,757
- Land of the Micmacs.
- Micmacs?

449
00:59:04,266 --> 00:59:06,564
Sounds too cold for me.

450
00:59:08,304 --> 00:59:12,764
- Must be purty country though.
