451
00:59:14,944 --> 00:59:16,343
Purty.

452
00:59:18,781 --> 00:59:20,874
Thank you very much.

453
00:59:21,050 --> 00:59:25,248
OK, now, let's have...
Omri and Patrick.

454
00:59:25,421 --> 00:59:28,322
I'll do it!
